Description: CANopen: Overflow internal receivequeue (message lost)Parameter _WarnLatched Bit 21
Cause: Two short CAN messages have beensent too fast (at 1 Mbits only).

Description: CANopen: CAN Controller in stateError PassiveParameter _WarnLatched Bit 21
Cause: Too many error frames have beendetected.

Description: CANopen: Detected Heartbeat or LifeGuard errorParameter _SigLatched Bit 21
Cause: The bus cycle time of the CANopenmaster is longer than theprogrammed heartbeat or nodeguarding time.
Correctives: Verify the CANopen configuration,increase the heartbeat or nodeguarding time.
